Modules

### 1. Donor Management Module

* Adds new donor details
* Validates donor age (18–65 years)
* Stores donor information in memory

### 2. View Donors Module

* Displays all registered donors
* Shows details like ID, name, age, blood group, and contact

### 3. Search Module

* Searches donors based on blood group
* Displays matching donor records

### 4. User Interface Module

* Menu-driven interface
* Handles user input and navigation
